{"tid":1670300,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港蓋世太保已成立，每日捉拿港人返密室虐殺","createTime":"2019-10-23T03:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T03:18:10.000Z","uid":34241,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"314edcce6822f777d4430639bb14b623b3664f0c","tid":1670300,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">休班警撩交嗌 誘捕5學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670213</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出現了<br />\n大家最期待既畫面出現了<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em>今次受害者係學生</em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一群自稱休班警察、無法出示任何可驗證身份既人類當眾襲擊、嚴重傷害他人身體、召來大批武裝恐怖份子恐嚇在場人士，<br />\n全部帶返密室虐殺<br />\n若干日後受害者全部都會被自殺，被跳海</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今次好彩有鏡頭，有街坊<br />\n下次無咁好彩了<br />\n冇鏡頭，冇人圍觀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>就地格殺你都冇人知</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人<br />\n準備好隨時當街被虐殺未？！！<br />\n你當場被殺，唔會有機會伸冤<br />\n<br />\n你冚家都會被虐殺</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點算好呢？<br />\n繼續快樂抗爭、和平抗爭嗎？"},{"pid":"9dc0f6813e1f8b68a22bbb626c1d826d3344a4f4","tid":1670300,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"搵我？"},{"pid":"8e2226be64816f84860804e90b087de11919968f","tid":1670300,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:03:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"964951839a6dedcb8fffdbd2c7697ab9d356bb20","tid":1670300,"uid":279356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4rWyof9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4rWyof9.gif&h=0c250780&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"861282362d0e5ff562954ba7e2e3f509f12bc766","tid":1670300,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dc0f6813e1f8b68a22bbb626c1d826d3344a4f4","tid":1670300,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"搵我？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人要真。反抗<br />\n就地攻擊恐怖份子<br />\n格殺恐怖份子無罪！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f64efbc6c37c1c107ec352a1c5a6fcf573988cac","tid":1670300,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=e994baad\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=7d7c46d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=4c7169dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=266f0aba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"e2e2167ce74be67e94f44acc5a14fdf09dbccb29","tid":1670300,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,